edding Insurance","hilda_services_insurance_description":"Protecting your investment from circumstances beyond your control that may cancel your wedding*","hilda_app_title":"Download The App and Get Started Now!","hilda_app_subtitle":"Chat with Hilda on Bridestory App !","hilda_app_dowload":"Download Bridestory App and get Hilda as your personal wedding consultant now!","hilda_challenge_title":"Challenge Our Price","hilda_challenge_subtitle":"and get instant cash if you found a better deal!","hilda_challenge_button":"Learn More","hilda_testimonials_title":"Testimonials","hilda_testimonials_1":"Hilda is very responsive and helpful, the special rate they could get from vendors helps me get closer to my dream wedding without stretching my budget.","hilda_testimonials_2":"Hilda helps us to find best suitable vendors for our needs and even helped us get the best price. Great assistant for ur wedding needs!","hilda_testimonials_3":"HILDA helps my wedding preparation becoming an enjoyable and stress-free experience. The best part is the best deals that HILDA offers!","hilda_testimonials_4":"HILDA makes my life a lot easier in finding vendors that suits my criteria and budget. The best part is, I can get huge discount from vendors through HILDA!","hilda_testimonials_5":"HILDA sangat memudahkan wedding planning sehingga kami tidak menjadi groomster dan bridezilla. Excellent service that comes with best deal!","hilda_testimonials_6":"Hilda is able to answer numerous all-soon-to-be-newly-weds questions that we have. The experience and attitude of service is one of the most important thing.","hilda_testimonials_7":"Hilda has helped me in a lot of ways: starting from vendor selections until the perfect execution Hilda is always there. Truly like a good friend, more than a wedding assistant.","hilda_testimonials_8":"Hilda was really helpful and it saves a lot of my time. Thank you for making everything that seems impossible became possible, and help me not turning into a scary bridezilla!","hilda_faqs_title":"FAQs","hilda_faqs_more":"View More FAQs","hilda_weddings_title":"Weddings Assisted by Hilda","hilda_wedding_link":"See The Wedding","hilda_challenge_popup_title":"Price Challenge","hilda_challenge_popup_subtitle":"How to Challenge Our Best Deal Guarantee and <strong>Get IDR 2,000,000</strong> When You Find A Better Deal","hilda_challenge_popup_download":"Download Bridestory App","hilda_challenge_1":"Download <strong>Bridestory App</strong> and chat with <strong>Hilda</strong>","hilda_challenge_2":"Discuss, negotiate, and get your final quotation directly from the vendors that you want to book","hilda_challenge_3":"Tell <strong>Hilda</strong> your final quotation and let <strong>Hilda</strong> get back to you with her offer.","hilda_challenge_4":"If <strong>Hilda</strong> is not able to better your final quotation, you will be entitled for <strong>IDR 2,000,000</strong> cash!","hilda_challenge_tnc":"Terms &amp; Conditions","hilda_challenge_tnc_apply":"applies","hilda_challenge_tnc_1":"This challenge is not applicable for friends and/or family of the vendor.","hilda_challenge_tnc_2":"Final quotation has to be in written form with the vendor's letter-pad, can be digitally typed, clearly addressed your event’s details, including your name, your partner’s name, event date, services included, menu, no. of pax and any other relevant details, within the same time horizon and event size.","hilda_challenge_tnc_3":"Final quotation has to include any relevant tax and service charge, if any.","hilda_challenge_tnc_4":"If you truly get a better deal than Hilda, the IDR 2,000,000 payment will be made via bank transfer on the first business day after your event date.","hilda_challenge_tnc_5":"This challenge does not apply if:","hilda_challenge_tnc_5_1":"You have approached the vendor directly before being introduced by Hilda.","hilda_challenge_tnc_5_2":"Your booking is cancelled, refunded, or changed.","hilda_challenge_tnc_5_3":"The final quotation submitted for claim is out-of-date.","hilda_challenge_tnc_6":"Only applicable to Hilda Business Partner vendors.","hilda_challenge_tnc_7":"<strong>Hilda by Bridestory</strong> has the right and discretion to determine the validity of any claim, including but not limited to determine that it meets all terms, conditions, and claims processing requirements.","hilda_challenge_tnc_8":"<strong>Hilda by Bridestory</strong> has the right to modify or discontinue Best Deal Guarantee Challenge or restrict its availability to any person, at any time, for any or no reason, and without prior notice or agreement.","assisted_by":"Dibantu","hilda_booked_through":"Dipesan Melalui","bspay_badge_title":"Cicilan 0&percnt; hingga 24 bulan","bspay_badge_title_short":"Cicilan 0&percnt;","bspay_badge_btn_learn":"Pelajari","bspay_badge_btn_chat":"Chat","bspay_badge_caption":"<strong>Cicilan 0&percnt;</strong> dengan <strong>Bridestory Pay</strong>","bspay_badge_caption_plain":"Cicilan 0&percnt; dengan Bridestory Pay","bspay_badge_description":" Vendor menerima metode pembayaran cicilan 0&percnt; hingga 24 bulan untuk semua transaksi menggunakan Bridestory Pay. Chat dengan vendor ini dan dapatkan penawaran terbaik sekarang.","bspay_badge_cashback":"Cashback hingga Rp 1 juta","bspay_badge_cashback_sg":"Cashback hingga SGD 100","bspay_badge_more_payments":"Opsi pembayaran lebih banyak","bspay_badge_cashback_short":"Cashback","bspay_badge_cancellation":"Gratis Asuransi Pernikahan","bspay_badge_btn_ask":"Minta Quotation","bspay_ask_quotation_value":"Hai, bisakah saya mendapatkan penawaran untuk layanan Anda? Saya tertarik untuk membayar melalui Bridestory Pay.","bspay_badge_filter_label":"Hanya menampilkan Bridestory Pay Vendor","forgot_password_all_required":"Semua harus diisi"},"device":"desktop","localization":"ID","translation":"id","availableLanguages":["en","id"],"allAvailableLanguages":["en","id"],"availableLocalization":["ID","SG","PH"],"gitHash":"3a38897"};
