rsebut tidak akan menghapuskan keabsahan dan keberlakuan dari ketentuan lainnya dalam Syarat dan Ketentuan Pengguna ini. Dengan demikian ketentuan lainnya dalam Syarat dan Ketentuan Pengguna ini akan tetap berlaku sepenuhnya secara sah terlepas dari ketentuan yang dianggap tidak sah, tidak berlaku, tidak dapat dilaksanakan atau melanggar hukum tersebut.</span></p>","tnc_label_updated_tnc_sg":"User Terms and Conditions last updated September 14th 2018","tnc_desc_sg":"<p class=\"f-g-14 mt-10\"><h2 class=\"f-b-14 mt-20\">GENERAL TERMS</h2></p><p class=\"f-g-14 mt-20\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Terms and Conditions as specified below (hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;</span><strong>User Terms and Conditions</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&rdquo;) applies to your usage of the Bridestory&rsquo;s platform that you can access including but not limited to the website </span><a href=\"http://www.bridestory.com\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">www.bridestory.com</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and through mobile applications \"android\" or \"ios\" (&ldquo;</span><strong>Bridestory Platform</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\") which is owned and managed by <strong>Bridestory Singapore Pte. Ltd. (Registration No 201607112H)</strong>, a limited liability company existing under the laws of the Republic of Singapore having its registered office at 1 Raffles Place #18-61, One Raffles Place Tower 2. Singapore 048616 doing business as Bridestory and hereafter referred to as (&ldquo;</span><strong>Bridestory</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\")</span></p><p class=\"f-g-14 mt-10\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In order for you to be able to use the facilities provided by Bridestory Platform completely, then you must first register in advance by creating an account on Bridestory Platform as a User (as defined below) and you represent and warrant that you are an individual who is legally entitled to hold a binding agreement based o